WEBVTT

00:00.264 --> 00:02.920
<i>My name is Michael Westen.</i>
<i>I used to be a spy until...</i>

00:04.305 --> 00:05.739
We got a burn notice
on you. You're blacklisted.

00:07.627 --> 00:09.961
<i>When you're burned,</i>
<i>you've got nothing --</i>

00:10.029 --> 00:12.230
<i>no cash, no credit,</i>
<i>no job history.</i>

00:12.298 --> 00:14.633
<i>You're stuck in whatever city</i>
<i>they decide to dump you in.</i>

00:14.701 --> 00:16.501
- Where am I?
- Miami.

00:16.569 --> 00:19.304
<i>You do whatever work</i>
<i>comes your way.</i>

00:19.372 --> 00:21.406
<i>You rely on anyone</i>
<i>who's still talking to you.</i>

00:22.508 --> 00:23.875
<i>A trigger-happy girlfriend...</i>

00:23.943 --> 00:25.510
Should we shoot them?

00:25.578 --> 00:27.312
<i>...an old friend who used</i>
<i>to inform on you to the FBI...</i>

00:27.380 --> 00:30.082
You know spies --
a bunch of bitchy little girls.

00:30.149 --> 00:32.451
<i>...family, too...</i>
<i>Hey, is that your mom again?</i>

00:32.518 --> 00:34.386
<i>...if you're desperate....</i>
<i>Someone needs your help, Michael.</i>

00:34.454 --> 00:37.522
<i>...and a down-and-out spy</i>
<i>you met along the way.</i>

00:37.590 --> 00:39.157
That's how we do it,
people.

00:39.225 --> 00:41.827
<i>Bottom line --</i>
<i>as long as you're burned,</i>

00:41.894 --> 00:47.099
<i>you're not going anywhere.</i>

00:49.736 --> 00:51.303
Nate!

00:51.370 --> 00:52.771
I'm sorry.

00:52.839 --> 00:55.240
No!
Nate!

00:55.308 --> 00:56.508
Nate's gone.

00:56.576 --> 00:57.776
No, he isn't!

