01:06.953 --> 01:08.553
Whatever leads the FBI
had on Nate's murder

01:08.621 --> 01:10.922
are now
in a sealed case file.

01:10.990 --> 01:12.124
Well,
we don't have the shooter,

01:12.191 --> 01:12.991
but we do have
the sniper rifle --

01:13.059 --> 01:14.893
the sale order shows

01:14.961 --> 01:16.027
the gun landed
at the Pryon Group.

01:16.095 --> 01:18.396
It's a private security firm
upstate.

01:18.464 --> 01:19.564
We have to
get a meeting

01:19.632 --> 01:21.233
with the guy
who runs the Pryon Group.

01:21.300 --> 01:24.002
He asked for a sniper
cleared on five different guns.

01:24.070 --> 01:25.370
Did you think
I wouldn't figure out

01:25.438 --> 01:26.471
you're looking for Tyler Gray?

01:26.539 --> 01:28.373
Tyler Gray?

01:34.113 --> 01:35.781
Who's Tyler Gray?

01:35.848 --> 01:37.149
Who's Tyler Gray?!

01:43.923 --> 01:47.359
<i>Whenever you get a fresh piece</i>
<i>of intelligence in the field,</i>

01:47.426 --> 01:49.161
<i>you have to decide carefully</i>

01:49.228 --> 01:50.729
<i>who you're going to</i>
<i>share it with,</i>

01:50.797 --> 01:54.099
<i>because every asset you</i>
<i>talk to, agency you work with,</i>

01:54.167 --> 01:57.636
<i>and resource you update brings</i>
<i>along a new set of problems.</i>

01:58.905 --> 02:01.973
Michael, what the hell
were you thinking

02:02.041 --> 02:03.441
bringing the CIA
into this?

02:03.509 --> 02:04.743
Fi,
I guess Sam told you.

02:04.811 --> 02:06.444
Yeah, well, I guess
he's not as comfortable

02:06.512 --> 02:08.413
lying to me
as some people are.

02:10.935 --> 02:13.203
This is a huge mistake,
Michael.

02:13.271 --> 02:14.471
A huge mistake.

02:14.539 --> 02:16.640
I didn't have a choice here.
I had to.

02:16.708 --> 02:19.376
We hit a wall,
and I needed the resources.

02:19.444 --> 02:20.844
You know as well as I do

02:20.912 --> 02:22.813
their resources
come with strings.

02:22.880 --> 02:24.247
And every time
we involve them,

02:24.315 --> 02:25.749
everything
gets more complicated!

02:25.817 --> 02:28.051
Fi, you suggested
I call the CIA.

02:28.119 --> 02:29.219
Well,
that was before

02:29.287 --> 02:30.187
they ruined
Agent Pearce's career.

02:30.254 --> 02:30.793
I'm sorry, Fi,

02:30.794 --> 02:32.895
but I'm not gonna let the man
who killed my brother get away.

02:32.962 --> 02:34.763
I don't care
who I have to work with.

02:36.599 --> 02:38.199
How do you know
they can even help?

02:38.267 --> 02:39.434
What makes you think

02:39.502 --> 02:41.536
they can find anything more
than we have?

02:41.604 --> 02:43.238
Because they already did.
Card just called me.

02:43.305 --> 02:44.105
I'm meeting him
in an hour.

02:55.584 --> 02:57.519
You, get me a dedicated
comm-link up and going.

02:57.586 --> 03:00.588
You, get me an upgraded grid
of all local law enforcement

03:00.656 --> 03:02.223
in the area.

03:02.291 --> 03:04.325
And, you, get with D.O.D. and
see if we have eyes in the sky.

03:04.393 --> 03:08.563
And, you, come with me.
What do you have?

03:08.631 --> 03:09.697
I took
your Tyler Gray file,

03:09.765 --> 03:11.299
gave it to
one of my tech geeks,

03:11.367 --> 03:13.468
and they fed the specs into
the FBI/CIA Interpol database.

03:13.536 --> 03:18.173
Nearly 1,000 partial matches
came back --

03:18.240 --> 03:21.543
photos of people who shared even
the tiniest detail with Gray.

03:21.610 --> 03:23.878
1,000? That's a big pond
to be fishing in.

03:23.946 --> 03:26.314
I tasked some low-level
gremlins at the NSA

03:26.382 --> 03:28.450
to use one of
their supercomputers

03:28.517 --> 03:32.587
to scour every shred of video
on the global system.

03:32.655 --> 03:34.222
In just under
27 hours.

03:34.290 --> 03:35.390
Pay dirt.

03:38.327 --> 03:42.197
This is a munitions warehouse
in San Miguelito, Panama.

03:42.264 --> 03:44.899
At 2:59 a.m.,
this gentleman breaks in,

03:44.967 --> 03:46.601
steals several weapons,

03:46.669 --> 03:49.070
including a Barrett
sniper rifle,

03:49.138 --> 03:52.040
a known favorite of --
Tyler Gray.

03:52.108 --> 03:54.142
Same guy flies out of Newark
using a different name

03:54.210 --> 03:57.479
three hours after your brother,
Nate, was murdered.

03:57.546 --> 03:58.980
Now for
the glamour shot.

04:04.687 --> 04:05.987
Would you please say hello

04:06.055 --> 04:08.490
to the man who murdered
your brother Nate?

04:13.506 --> 04:17.505
<font color=#00FF00>Burn Notice 6x10</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Desperate Times</font>
